headline: WrestleMania速 41 in Las Vegas Becomes Most Successful Event in WWE History
summary: STAMFORD, Conn., April 22, 2025--WWE速, part of TKO Group Holdings (NYSE: TKO), today announced that WrestleMania 41, which emanated from Allegiant Stadium in Las Vegas, became the most-successful and highest-grossing event in company history.
